posting_body: ['REF# 10R180', '$3000 · Brickell · Unfurnished · 1/1 · The Axis On Brickell Cond · 693 Sqft', 'Call ➟ Text ➟ WhatsApp', "📲 786'*'5O5'*'4314", 'Carlos Manchego', 'Goldstein Realty', 'show contact info', 'Spacious 1 bed / 1 bath condo located in the heart of Brickell.', 'Complete with white porcelain floor (no carpet), top of the line appliances, and a beautiful balcony.', 'The bathroom features a separate tub and tastefully renovated shower.', 'Large bedroom with balcony access and walk-in closet.', 'The building, AXIS, is well known for its wonderful amenities: two pools, jacuzzi, state of the art gym, WIFI service in common areas, game room, play ground, kids room, conference room, party room, pool tables, valet parking available, a must see!', 'Axis association requires $500 deposit for common areas.', 'Read Less', 'REF# 10R180', 'tags:', 'vizcayne, isola, bay point homes, villaggio in the grove, the vue at brickell condo, park grove, bay point homes, bayshore place condo, icon brickell one, two midtown, brickell key one, ios on the bay, carbonell condo, madison downtown condo, brickell east condo, the palace, costa bella, nine at mary brickell village, the grove club condo, marina blue, villa regina condo, direct bay view, 23 biscayne bay condo, epic residences, bayfront homes in miami, fortune house, the mutiny, grovenor house, the palace, cynergi, brand new, 50 biscayne,, brickell bay club, brickell vista', '_mr10']
